'''特洛伊·希文·梅萊'''（{{lang-en|Troye Sivan Mellet}}，{{IPAc-en|t|r|ɔɪ|_|s|ᵻ|ˈ|v|ɑː|n}}，{{bd|1995年|6月5日}}）是一位[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[創作型歌手|創作型歌手]]、[[演員|演員]]及[[YouTuber|YouTuber]]。作为YouTube名人，希文于2007年创建了自己的YouTube频道“TroyeSivan18”，定期上传视频，截至2018年4月已经拥有610万订阅者，视频总播放量超过2.7亿次。<ref name="Social Blade">{{cite web |url=http://socialblade.com/youtube/user/troyesivan18 |title=Troyesivan18 YouTube Stats, Channel Statistics |publisher=Social Blade |accessdate=2015-08-23 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028231928/https://socialblade.com/youtube/user/troyesivan18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而作为演员，希文在2009年的[[X战警|X战警]]系列电影《[[X戰警：金鋼狼|X戰警：金鋼狼]]》中出演了少年时期的[[金鋼狼|詹姆斯·豪利特]]，之后又主演了南非电影《{{le|马铃薯 (电影)|Spud (film)|马铃薯}}》三部曲。

2013年6月，希文以歌手的身份与[[百代唱片|澳洲百代唱片]]签约，并在2014年8月15日发行了首张主流厂牌[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《{{le|TRXYE|TRXYE}}》。专辑发行后在美国[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上最高排名第5位。<ref>{{cite web|first=Alex|last=Frank|url=http://www.thefader.com/2015/09/04/troye-sivan-wild-interview|title=Troye Sivan: “I Just Wanted To Write Normal Pop Songs And Use The Word ‘He’”|work=The Fader magazine|date=September 4, 2015|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009011752/http://www.thefader.com/2015/09/04/troye-sivan-wild-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑的首支单曲《Happy Little Pill》也登上[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳大利亚单曲榜]]的第10位和新西兰单曲榜的第2位。2015年9月，希文发行了自己的第二张主流厂牌迷你专辑《{{le|Wild (迷你专辑)|Wild (Troye Sivan EP)|Wild}}》；同年12月4日发行了首张录音室专辑《{{le|Blue Neighbourhood|Blue Neighbourhood}}》。专辑获得乐评界的好评，在美国公告牌二百强专辑榜上最高排名第7位。

2014年，希文凭借与另一位YouTube名人[[泰勒·奥克利|泰勒·奥克利]]合作的视频《The 'Boyfriend' Tag》获得当年[[青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]的“最受欢迎网络合作”奖。2014年10月，《[[时代杂志|时代]]》杂志将希文列为“2014年最有影响力的25位青少年”之一。<ref>{{cite news |title=The 25 Most Influential Teens of 2014 |url=http://time.com/3486048/most-influential-teens-2014/ |website=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=2014-10-13 |accessdate=2015-08-23 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VJ9l0sZQ?url=http://time.com/3486048/most-influential-teens-2014/ |archivedate=2015-01-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>2014年11月还被美国同性恋时尚杂志《[[Out_(杂志)|OUT]]》评为“2014年OUT杂志百大人物”之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2014/2014/11/03/out100-troye-sivan|title=OUT100: Troye Sivan|work=Out|date=2014-11-03|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2017-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016000915/https://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2014/2014/11/03/out100-troye-sivan|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年和2015年，希文先后两次被美国音乐杂志《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》评为“21位21岁以下的最佳歌手”（"21 Under 21"）之一，分别排名第17位和第6位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/21-under-21/6259308/21-under-21-2014-lorde-bieber-mahone-garrix-5-seconds-summer|title=21 Under 21 (2014): Music's Hottest Young Stars|work=Billboard|date=2014-09-24|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229091403/http://www.billboard.com/articles/21-under-21/6259308/21-under-21-2014-lorde-bieber-mahone-garrix-5-seconds-summer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/photos/6745079/billboard-21-under-21-2015-hottest-young-stars/8|title=Billboard's 21 Under 21 2015: Music's Hottest Young Stars|work=Billboard|date=2015-10-31|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2016-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126050145/http://www.billboard.com/photos/6745079/billboard-21-under-21-2015-hottest-young-stars/8|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年生活==
希文出生於[[南非|南非]][[约翰内斯堡|约翰内斯堡]]的一個[[猶太教正統派|猶太教正統派]]家庭。<ref name="sign"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZTIH8FrqQyM |title=Australian Boy Does Accents! |publisher=YouTube |date=2012-11-17 |accessdate=2015-08-23 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016212148/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZTIH8FrqQyM |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="smh1">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/meet-aussie-troye-sivan-pops-newest-superstar-20140728-zxl36.html|title=Meet Aussie Troye Sivan, pop's newest superstar|work=[[悉尼先驱晨报|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|accessdate=2015-08-23|date=2014-07-28|first=George|last=Palathingal|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619213844/https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/meet-aussie-troye-sivan-pops-newest-superstar-20140728-zxl36.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的父亲肖恩·梅莱（Shaun Mellet）出生在一個[[立陶宛猶太人|立陶宛猶太人]]家庭，是一位[[地产代理|房地产中介]]；母亲劳瑞尔·梅莱（Laurelle Mellet）是一位家庭主妇，也皈依了[[犹太教|犹太教]]。<ref name="earbiscuit" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://troyesivan.tumblr.com/post/31919189880/how-jewish-are-you-like-are-you-orthodox-or-reform-or |title=Troye Sivan's Tumblr — How Jewish are you? Like are you orthodox or reform or? |publisher=Troyesivan.tumblr.com |date= |accessdate=2015-08-23 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006092111/http://troyesivan.tumblr.com/post/31919189880/how-jewish-are-you-like-are-you-orthodox-or-reform-or |dead-url=no }}</ref>在他两岁时，全家因南非犯罪率日益上升而搬到[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]居住。<ref name="earbiscuit">{{cite podcast |first1 = Rhett |last1 = McLaughlin |first2 = Charles |last2 = Neal |authorlink = Rhett and Link |title = Ep. 29 Troye Sivan |url = https://soundcloud.com/earbiscuits/ep-29-troye-sivan-ear-biscuits |publisher = Ear Biscuits |date = 2014-04-19 |accessdate = 2015-01-14 |archive-date = 2018-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180121182536/https://soundcloud.com/earbiscuits/ep-29-troye-sivan-ear-biscuits |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="BB Bio">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6222117/troye-sivan/biography|title=ARTISTS / Troye Sivan / Biography|work=Billboard|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204235600/https://www.billboard.com/artist/6222117/troye-sivan/biography|dead-url=no}}</ref>希文与父母和三个兄弟姐妹居住在[[西澳大利亚州|西澳大利亚州]]的[[珀斯|珀斯]]。<ref name="smh2">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/good-weekend/troye-sivan-the-most-famous-teenager-youve-never-heard-of-20150209-13a11r.html|title=Troye Sivan, the most famous teenager you've never heard of|date=2015-02-27|first=Benjamin|last=Law|6=|work=[[悉尼先驱晨报|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2018-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121182537/http://www.smh.com.au/good-weekend/troye-sivan-the-most-famous-teenager-youve-never-heard-of-20150209-13a11r.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Cameron|last=Adams|url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/music/youtube-sensation-troye-sivan-on-his-debut-album-being-gay-and-being-a-gay-role-model/news-story/9a1b34a13fa114f884d7eda12c0b69e6|title=YouTube sensation Troye Sivan on his debut album, being gay and being a gay role model|work=news-com-au|date=December 2, 2015|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121121804/https://www.news.com.au/entertainment/music/youtube-sensation-troye-sivan-on-his-debut-album-being-gay-and-being-a-gay-role-model/news-story/9a1b34a13fa114f884d7eda12c0b69e6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Jake|last=Hall|url=http://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/34393/1/troye-sivan-heaven-video-interview|title=TTroye Sivan on the queer politics of his new video|work=Dazed magazine|date=January 19, 2017|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807160350/https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/34393/1/troye-sivan-heaven-video-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Alex|last=Frank|url=http://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/39346/1/troye-sivan-boy-erased-new-album-interview|title=Troye Sivan: atomic blonde|work=Dazed magazine|date=March 14, 2018|accessdate=May 8, 2018|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319002649/https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/39346/1/troye-sivan-boy-erased-new-album-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>希文9岁左右直至13岁时一直接受专业的歌唱培训，他曾就读于珀斯当地的一家犹太人学校卡梅尔学校（Carmel School），2009年之后便开始在家自学，接受[[远程教育|远程教育]]。<ref>{{cite web |first=Gabrielle |last=Reilly |title=Troye Sivan Interview |url=http://www.theglobaltownhall.com/troye_sivan |website=The Global Townhall |accessdate=2015-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VZkds3Ph?url=http://www.theglobaltownhall.com/troye_sivan |archivedate=2015-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jewishnews.net.au/learning-from-luminaries/25751|title=Learning from luminaries|work=Australia Jewish News|date=2012-04-13|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629183045/https://www.jewishnews.net.au/learning-from-luminaries/25751|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="stm"/>

==音乐事业==
2006年至2008年，希文连续三年参加了[[七号电视网|七号电视网]]珀斯电视募捐活动（Channel Seven Perth Telethon），并在活动中献唱。这一活动是澳大利亚的七号电视网旗下电视台每年在珀斯举办的慈善活动，募得资金将捐献给珀斯当地的儿童医院、儿童健康研究院和听障中心等机构。<ref name="PerthNow">{{cite news|last=Symonds|first=Kristy|title=Perth boy making it big in Hollywood|url=http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/perth-boy-making-it-big-in-hollywood/story-e6frg30c-1226321060650|accessdate=2015-08-23|newspaper=Perth Now|date=2012-04-07|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708200045/http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/perth-boy-making-it-big-in-hollywood/story-e6frg30c-1226321060650|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="stm">{{cite news|last=Harvey|first=Shannon|title=Perth boy to play young Hugh Jackman in Wolverine movie|url=http://www.perthnow.com.au/news/perth-boy-to-play-young-hugh/story-e6frg12c-1111115680990|accessdate=2015-08-23|newspaper=Perth Now|date=2008-02-28|archive-date=2016-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912104156/http://www.perthnow.com.au/news/perth-boy-to-play-young-hugh/story-e6frg12c-1111115680990|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中，2006年的表演中，他还与《[[澳洲偶像|澳洲偶像]]》冠军{{le|盖伊·塞巴斯蒂安|Guy Sebastian}}合唱。<ref name="stm"/>2007年，他还参加了澳大利亚的真人秀节目StarSearch，并进入了总决赛。<ref name="PerthNow"/>同年，他还独立发行了自己的首张[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《Dare to Dream》，其中收录了五首翻唱歌曲。<ref name="BB Bio"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.last.fm/music/Troye+Sivan/Dare+To+Dream|title=Troye Sivan Dare To Dream|accessdate=2015-08-23|work=Last.fm|archive-date=2015-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151201060150/http://www.last.fm/music/Troye+Sivan/Dare+To+Dream|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[2010年海地地震|2010年海地地震]]后，YouTube名人[[藍莎·拉薇|藍莎·拉薇]]组织57位YouTube歌手共同翻唱了《[[四海一家25週年海地慈善版|四海一家25週年海地慈善版]]》以帮助地震灾区募捐，希文也参与了歌曲的表演和录制。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hhX0KkQBW4|title=We Are The World 25 For Haiti (YouTube Edition)|work=YouTube|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708233019/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hhX0KkQBW4|archivedate=2015-07-08}}</ref>2012年6月22日，希文又发行了个人的第二张迷你专辑《June Haverly》，收录了三首歌曲。<ref name="BB Bio"/><ref name="BandCamp">{{cite web|url=https://troyesivan.bandcamp.com/album/the-june-haverly-ep|title=The June Haverly EP by Troye Sivan|work=bandcamp.com|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325175659/http://troyesivan.bandcamp.com/album/the-june-haverly-ep|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年5月5日，希文在自己的YouTube频道上发布了原创歌曲《The Fault In Our Stars》。歌曲受到讲述癌症少年生活的小说《[[生命中的美好缺憾|生命中的美好缺憾]]》（The Fault In Our Stars）及其[[星运里的错|改编电影]]的启发，发售的全部收入捐献给了珀斯的玛格丽特公主医院基金会（Princess Margaret Hospital Foudation）作癌症治疗和研究之用。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OqG55HdmKTE|work=YouTube|title=The Fault In Our Stars - Troye Sivan (Official Music Video)|date=2013-05-05|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517175247/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OqG55HdmKTE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="smh2"/>歌曲发布之后获得巨大的成功和反响。<ref name="hlp"/><ref name="smh2"/>2013年6月5日，希文与[[环球唱片|澳洲环球唱片]]旗下的[[百代唱片|澳洲百代唱片]]签约，但直至一年之后才正式公开。2014年，他发行了自己的首张主流厂牌迷你专辑《{{le|TRXYE|TRXYE}}》，其中收录了包括《The Fault In Our Stars》在内的五首原创歌曲。专辑的首支单曲《Happy Little Pill》于7月25日发行，专辑则于8月15日正式发行。<ref name="smh1"/><ref name="sign">{{cite web|last1=Caulfield|first1=Keith|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6140809/youtube-star-troye-sivan-signs-with-emi-australia-announces-ep|title=YouTube Star Troye Sivan Signs With EMI Australia, Announces EP|website=Billboard|date=2014-06-27|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2018-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422204904/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6140809/youtube-star-troye-sivan-signs-with-emi-australia-announces-ep|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hlp">{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3034455/troye-sivan-single-happy-little-pill-youtube-star/|title=Hear YouTube Superstar Troye Sivan’s Single 'Happy Little Pill'|work=Time|date=2014-07-25|accessdate=2015-08-23|first=Abby|last=Abrams|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125024738/https://time.com/3034455/troye-sivan-single-happy-little-pill-youtube-star/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《TRXYE》一经发行便登上超过55个国家和地区的[[iTunes_Store|iTunes]]即时排行榜第一位。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stern|first1=Bradley|url=http://www.idolator.com/7531054/troye-sivan-shoots-to-1-on-itunes-with-debut-ep-trxye|title=Troye Sivan Shoots To #1 On iTunes (In 55 Countries!) With Debut EP, 'TRXYE'|website=Idolator|date=2014-08-15|accessdate=2015-08-23}}</ref>专辑获得广泛好评，随后登上美国[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]，首周排名第5位，也成为希文首张进入美国专辑排行榜前十位的专辑。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Caulfield|first1=Keith|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/6221699/troye-sivan-set-for-top-10-debut-on-billboard-200|title=Troye Sivan Set for Top 10 Debut on Billboard 200|website=Billboard|date=2014-08-15|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401070030/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/6221699/troye-sivan-set-for-top-10-debut-on-billboard-200|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑的首支单曲《Happy Little Pill》在[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳大利亚唱片业协会榜]]上最高排名第10位，在[[新西兰官方音乐榜|新西兰官方音乐榜]]上最高排名第2位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Happy+Little+Pill&cat=s|title=TROYE SIVAN - HAPPY LITTLE PILL (SONG)|work=Australian Charts|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2020-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200128204435/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Happy+Little+Pill&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Happy+Little+Pill&cat=s|title=TROYE SIVAN - HAPPY LITTLE PILL (SONG)|work=New Zealand Charts|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2018-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180225081732/http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Happy+Little+Pill&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>单曲在澳大利亚售出35,000张，获得[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]的“金唱片”认证。<ref name="ARIAcert"/>2015年，希文与德国[[DJ|DJ]]、电子音乐人[[Zedd|Zedd]]合作，演唱了歌曲《Papercut》，收录在Zedd的第二张专辑《{{le|True Colors (捷德专辑)|True Colors (Zedd album)|True Colors}}》中，歌曲同时是这张专辑的第三支单曲。<ref name="papercut">{{cite web|url=http://popcrush.com/troye-sivan-zedd-papercut-true-colors/|title=Troye Sivan Teams Up with Zedd on Moody 'True Colors' Gem, 'Papercut'|work=PopCrush|date=2015-05-20|accessdate=2015-08-23|first=Bradley|last=Stern|archive-date=2020-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310230339/https://popcrush.com/troye-sivan-zedd-papercut-true-colors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年7月25日，希文通过YouTube频道宣布自己将发行第二张主流厂牌迷你专辑《{{le|Wild (迷你专辑)|Wild (Troye Sivan EP)|Wild}}》，同时还公布了专辑封面。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8VdLNpH_ns|title=Announcing My Album.|work=YouTube|date=2015-07-25|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2019-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114131333/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8VdLNpH_ns|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BB Wild">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6642093/youtube-star-troye-sivan-announces-new-album-wild|title=YouTube Star Troye Sivan Announces New Album 'Wild'|first=Keith|last=Caulfield|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2015-07-26|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-date=2020-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430080912/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6642093/youtube-star-troye-sivan-announces-new-album-wild|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑于2015年9月4日发行，其中收录了六首歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/wild-ep/id1030886717|title=WILD - EP|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-04|work=iTunes US|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923063124/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/wild-ep/id1030886717|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/wild-ep/id1028351582|title=WILD - EP|date=2015-09-04|accessdate=2015-09-04|work=iTunes AU|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403033958/https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/wild-ep/id1028351582|dead-url=no}}</ref>这张迷你专辑在发行首周即登上澳大利亚唱片业协会榜的冠军位置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2015/09/12/troye-sivan-beats-out-iron-maiden-for-1-album-debut/|title=Troye Sivan Beats Out Iron Maiden For #1 Album Debut|work=TheMusic.com.au|date=2015-09-12|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2015-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921022416/http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2015/09/12/troye-sivan-beats-out-iron-maiden-for-1-album-debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在美国公告牌二百强专辑榜最高排名第5位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2015/09/18/troye-sivan-scores-5-album-debut-on-us-billboard-charts/|title=Troye Sivan Scores #5 Debut On US Billboard Charts|work=TheMusic.com.au|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923233226/http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2015/09/18/troye-sivan-scores-5-album-debut-on-us-billboard-charts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月到10月期间，希文连续发布了三支音乐录影带，合称为“Blue Neighbourhood 三部曲”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.justjared.com/2015/10/23/troye-sivan-debuts-talk-me-down-video-completing-blue-neighborhood-trilogy/|title=Troye Sivan Debuts 'Talk Me Down' Video, Completing 'Blue Neighborhood' Trilogy|work=JustJared|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2016-01-05}}</ref>，随后在10月15日宣布将发行首张录音室专辑。<ref name="BN">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6730087/troye-sivan-announces-debut-album-blue-neighbourhood-adds-tour-dates|title=Troye Sivan Announces Debut Album 'Blue Neighbourhood,' Adds Tour Dates|work=Billboard|date=2015-10-15|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611022725/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6730087/troye-sivan-announces-debut-album-blue-neighbourhood-adds-tour-dates|dead-url=no}}</ref>希文的首张录音室专辑《{{le|Blue Neighbourhood|Blue Neighbourhood}}》发行于2015年12月4日。<ref name="BN"/>发行后首周登上澳大利亚澳大利亚唱片业协会榜第6位和美国公告牌二百强专辑榜第7位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Blue+Neighbourhood&cat=a|title=TROYE SIVAN - BLUE NEIGHBOURHOOD (ALBUM)|work=australian-charts.com|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212143732/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Troye+Sivan&titel=Blue+Neighbourhood&cat=a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6812805/justin-bieber-adele-aria-charts|title=Justin Bieber Lands Second No. 1 Down Under, Adele's '25' Continues Hot Streak|work=Billboard|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019231417/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6812805/justin-bieber-adele-aria-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://themusic.com.au/news/all/2015/12/18/troye-sivans-new-album-cracks-top-ten-on-the-us-billboard-albums-chart/|title=Troye Sivan's New Album Cracks Top Ten On The US Billboard Albums Chart|work=TheMusic.com.au|date=2015-12-18|accessdate=2016-01-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6805727/adeles-25-no-1-on-billboard-200-album-chart-third-week-coldplay-a-head-full-of-dreams|title=Adele's '25' Rules for Third Week at No. 1, Coldplay Debuts at No. 2 on Billboard 200|work=Billboard|date=2015-12-13|accessdate=2016-01-05|archive-date=2016-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514111437/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6805727/adeles-25-no-1-on-billboard-200-album-chart-third-week-coldplay-a-head-full-of-dreams|dead-url=no}}</ref>这张专辑发行后获得了乐评界的好评和商业上的成功<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/blue-neighbourhood-mw0002890150|work=AllMusic|accessdate=2016-01-05|title=Troye Sivan - Blue Neighbourhood|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401042734/https://www.allmusic.com/album/blue-neighbourhood-mw0002890150|dead-url=no}}</ref>，截至2016年已在全球售出逾500,000张<ref name="ARIA">{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/awards/arias/flume-troye-sivan-and-sia-dominate-nominations-for-2016-aria-awards/news-story/3b6a9813f276a638afb32ea52f76a095|title=Flume, Troye Sivan and Sia dominate nominations for 2016 ARIA Awards|publisher=News.com.au|date=2016-10-05|accessdate=2016-10-05|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125172906/https://www.news.com.au/entertainment/awards/arias/flume-troye-sivan-and-sia-dominate-nominations-for-2016-aria-awards/news-story/3b6a9813f276a638afb32ea52f76a095|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在美澳两国获得金唱片认证<ref name="aucert"/><ref name="uscert"/>。2016年，他还凭借这张专辑及其中单曲获得{{le|澳大利亚唱片业协会音乐奖|ARIA Music Awards}}的五项提名，并获得包括“年度歌曲”在内的两项大奖。专辑的制作人和录音师也获得两个技术奖项提名。<ref name="ARIA"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/triplej/musicnews/s4548089.htm|title=Flume leads ARIA nominations and he's won three Artisan Awards already|publisher=ABC|date=2016-10-05|accessdate=2016-10-05|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109132545/http://www.abc.net.au/triplej/musicnews/s4548089.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ARIA2">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/nov/23/arias-2016-winners-full-list|title=Arias 2016: Flume, marriage equality and lockout laws dominate music awards|publisher=The Guardian|date=2016-11-23|accessdate=2016-11-24|archive-date=2021-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401090323/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2016/nov/23/arias-2016-winners-full-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年1月10日，希文发行了单曲《My My My!》及音乐录影带。<ref name="NPR MyMyMy">{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/event/music/577378024/in-my-my-my-video-troye-sivan-cements-his-image-as-a-gay-pop-icon|title=In 'My My My!' Video, Troye Sivan Cements His Image As A Gay Pop Icon|work=NPR.org|access-date=2018-01-11|archive-date=2018-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614071801/https://www.npr.org/event/music/577378024/in-my-my-my-video-troye-sivan-cements-his-image-as-a-gay-pop-icon|dead-url=no}}</ref>乐评网站[[Pitchfork|Pitchfork]]将歌曲评为当周“最佳新歌”<ref>{{cite web|title=“My My My!” by Troye Sivan Review|url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/troye-sivan-my-my-my/|website=Pitchfork|accessdate=2018-01-13|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125114120/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/troye-sivan-my-my-my/|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]则认为这首歌彰显了希文对自己性取向的自信，为他确立了“[[同志偶像|同志偶像]]”的地位。<ref name="NPR MyMyMy"/>随后他于19日发行单曲《The Good Side》，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8094942/troye-sivan-the-good-side-new-song|title=Troye Sivan Gets the 'The Good Side' of Things in New Ballad|date=2018-01-18|publisher=Billboard|access-date=2018-01-20|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403090648/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8094942/troye-sivan-the-good-side-new-song|dead-url=no}}</ref>并于20日首次登上《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》的舞台表演。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-will-make-his-snl-debut-this-month|title=Troye Sivan Will Make His SNL Debut This Month|publisher=MTV UK|date=2018-01-12|accessdate=2018-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115212952/http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-will-make-his-snl-debut-this-month|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月19日，希文擔任美國創作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]的[[舉世盛名體育場巡迴演唱會|舉世盛名體育場巡迴演唱會]]驚喜嘉賓，泰勒絲在演唱會中替希文宣傳第二张专辑《[[綻放_(特洛伊·希文專輯)|绽放]]》于同年8月31日发行，之後希文也表示泰勒絲在發行《綻放》之前有事先聽過整張專輯，並給希文很多很好的建議，專輯發行之后获得广泛好评。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-bloom-album-review | title = Troye Sivan 'Bloom': Track By Track Album Review | work = MTV | last = Downing | first = Megan | date = 2018-08-29 | accessdate = 2018-08-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180831035500/http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-bloom-album-review | archive-date = 2018-08-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>他参与了2018年电影《[[爱你的西蒙|-{zh-cn:爱你的西蒙; zh-tw:親愛的初戀; zh-hk:抱抱我的初戀;}-]]》的原声带，在其中献唱歌曲《Strawberries & Cigarettes》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-joins-love-simon-soundtrack-with-new-song|title=Troye Sivan Joins 'Love, Simon' Soundtrack With New Song|publisher=MTV UK|date=2018-01-17|access-date=2018-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128154340/http://www.mtv.co.uk/troye-sivan/news/troye-sivan-joins-love-simon-soundtrack-with-new-song|dead-url=no}}</ref>还为自己出演的电影《[[被抹去的男孩|被抹去的男孩]]》献唱歌曲《Revelation》並首度入圍金球獎「最佳原創歌曲」。

2020年8月21號，澳洲環球音樂發行了第五張EP《In a Dream》是特洛伊在防疫居家時的創作， 其中主打歌曲之一《Take Yourself Home》還與藝術家Tony Galloway合作特製屬於台灣的繁體中文版歌詞MV。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UjLOGDH5uMw&feature=youtu.be|title=Troye Sivan - Take Yourself Home (Traditional Chinese Lyrics Video)|publisher=YouTube|date=2020-05-14}}</ref>

