2010年，希文还出演了西澳州制作的[[萨缪尔·贝克特|萨缪尔·贝克特]]创作的[[荒诞派戏剧|荒诞派戏剧]]《[[等待戈多|等待戈多]]》。戏剧自5月28日起上演，希文和另一位演员克雷格·海德-史密斯（Craig Hyde-Smith）在剧中交替饰演“小男孩”一角。<ref>{{cite news |title=Troye on stage with theatre great |first=Daniel |last=Hatch |url=http://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/a/-/breaking/7281062/troye-on-stage-with-theatre-great/ |newspaper=The West Australian |page=3 |date=2010-05-24 |accessdate=2015-08-24 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5pxoNqRIv?url=http://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/a/-/breaking/7281062/troye-on-stage-with-theatre-great/ |archivedate=2010-05-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="smh2"/>2012年6月，希文又回到南非出演《马铃薯》的续集《马铃薯2：疯狂无极限》（Spud 2: The Madness Continues），电影于2013年6月21日在南非上映。<ref name="smh1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://you.co.za/entertainment/interviews-with-the-cast-of-spud-troye-sivan-spud/|title=Spud 2: Getting to know . . . Troye Sivan|work=You.co.za|date=2013-06-20|accessdate=2015-08-24|first=Kirstin|last=Buick|archive-date=2017-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507035609/http://www.you.co.za/entertainment/interviews-with-the-cast-of-spud-troye-sivan-spud/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还继续主演了这一系列电影的第三部《马铃薯3：毕业季学会高飞》（Spud 3: Learning to Fly），电影于2014年11月28日上映。<ref name="smh1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://teneightymagazine.com/2014/09/23/caspar-lee-and-troye-sivan-film-trailer-released/|title=Caspar Lee And Troye Sivan Film Trailer Released|work=TenEighty|accessdate=2015-08-24|first=Alex J|last=Brinnand|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031130734/https://teneightymagazine.com/2014/09/23/caspar-lee-and-troye-sivan-film-trailer-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

